OL,3,COutrage after council asks paralysed
OL,4,Cgrandad to 'blink' to end tenancy
OL,5,Cagreement
OL,7,FA family from Hampshire say they're
OL,8,Ffurious after their paralysed father
OL,9,Fwas asked to 'blink' in order to get
OL,10,Fout of his tenancy agreement.
OL,12,FPeter Badger was left unable to move
OL,13,For talk after suffering two brain
OL,14,Fbleeds.
OL,16,FHis daughters tried to cancel the
OL,17,Ftenancy of the flat he can no longer
OL,18,Flive in, but Southampton City Council
OL,19,Fsaid they needed confirmation direct
OL,20,Ffrom Peter, suggesting he blink at a
OL,21,Fhousing officer.
