OL,7,FThe local authority has since
OL,8,Fapologised for the delays and distress
OL,9,Fand promised to review its procedures.
OL,11,FPeter's daughter, Amber, said: "I
OL,12,Fcompletely understand that there are
OL,13,Fprocesses and laws and things that
OL,14,Fneed to be followed, but there was no
OL,15,Fcompassion.
OL,17,F"It was, we were just another tick
OL,18,Fbox, and that was really hard to add
OL,19,Fin with everything that we were
OL,20,Fdealing with anyway."
